Starscram

Starscream was about to go nuts.

"EVERYONE BE QUIET! Look at us. Fighting amongst each other, pretty 
soon it will come to fighting. Atma Pseudo and Technosis have already 
left. You've got to be thinking that those Maximals are just laughing 
it up! This is what they want, us to go against each other and kill 
ourselves. We have to focus on goals here. Our first goal: Get KitKat 
better. Now, if we go with Tarantulas, we'll get KitKat better. But 
she wants to go with the Alliance. So what is the point of going with 
Tarantulas when we would be leaving there later. I say we just go 
with the Alliance and get KitKat repaired. I could use some repairs 
too. Sharp pains are gowing through me every time I move, and their 
getting worse. So let's jsut go with Bolldystrike.
